cdata.name: Graft Blockchain
cdata.desc:
A first global, open sourced, payment gateway blockchain network designed for Point-of-Sale.

The Graft Blockchain is powered by the Graft token (GRF). The GRFtoken will enable purchasers to transact and operate services on the Graft platform when it is launched. GRF is required for participation in Graft network activities.
